25|$|In a {{standard}} termination, all accrued benefits {{under the plan}} become 100% vested. The plan must purchase <b>annuity</b> <b>contracts</b> for all participants. If the plan permits the payment of lump sums, employees may be offered {{the choice of a}} lump sum payment or an annuity.|$|R
